There is an emergency closure of US 2 northeast of Wenatchee from MP 142 to MP 144 just west of Waterville due to a rock slide in Pine Canyon. There are no official detours but alternative routes for non-freight travel are available on McNeil Canyon Rd. and Badger Mountain Rd. The road is scheduled to be reopened no later than March 25.Contact: Project Engineer James Reynolds 509-667-2861
